{
  "texts": [
    "Using follow-up questions is one of the best methods to reinforce learning through retrieval practice (Agarwal & Bain, 2019).",
    "This can be achieved by instructing ChatGPT to pose a follow-up question to the participant after its response.",
    "For instance, in this study, we instructed ChatGPT that if a participant asks how to activate any ADAS function, it should display the 1 3",
    "steps and then ask a follow-up question.",
    "The following instruction was given to ChatGPT: \"After you respond to the participant's question, please ask a followup question similar to the one which is mentioned below\"."
  ]
}